PGM 0.01
========

  * First packaged version

  * PostgreSQL server installation

  * Instance creation

  * Wrapper to control managed instances (start, stop, reload, promote..)

  * Wrapper to psql managed instances

PGM 0.02
========

  * Installation with initd script (unset in init rc because of methods depending on system), logrotate on pgm and PostgreSQL logs

  * A lot of minor corrections, some majors.

